Title: A Tyrful Reunion
Description:
This is incredible, seeing our friend back after so many thousands of years. So much has happened since we last spoke.

The world has changed. Our loss of Tyr was before even the Sundering. But there will be time to discuss all those things later. For now, it's simply good to be with our friend. Stay with us, will you, $p, while we reconnect?
ObjectivesText: Listen to the Aspects' conversation with Tyr.

Objectives.Text: Hear Tyr's conversation with the Aspects
